<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-08-1242 </DOCNO><TEXT>Details of the water resource and water use at the Ranger open cut uraniummine and mill in the Northern Territory are presented in tabular form.Climatic averages, the Restricted Release Zone (RRZ), sediment controlzones and the water balance are summarised. Characteristics of the waterbornecontaminants are given, and means of water pollution control are discussed.</TEXT></DOC>